string_about_summary: Instander is a free modification of the Instagram app for android. It contains many improvements over the original application.
string_feature_summary: Instander has a lot of different improvements that give the user an edge over other Instagram users. These are the main features of Instander:
string_ads_summary: Completely free app with no Instagram ads
string_downloader_summary: Download photos, videos, stories and IGTV with ease
string_hq_summary: Upload your photos and stories with better quality
string_privacy_summary: View stories, read and write messages without anyone's knowledge
string_versions_summary: There are 2 versions of the application, the original and the clone.
string_orig_summary: Requires the removal of the official Instagram application. It supports integration with other apps.
string_clone_summary: Allows you to install next to the official app. It has a different icon and application name.
